## Domain Knowledge
- Fiscal year ends June 30 (pre-1976) or September 30 (post-1976). Calendar year ends December 31.
- Data for period X appears in bulletins published AFTER period X.
- October/September bulletins are richest. Check table unit headers.
- Read row labels exactly: "total gross federal debt" ≠ "public debt outstanding."

